---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Home" description="Project UNAC is a black-canvas world archive and music portal by SHINHWI.">
  <section class="hero-type-band home-hero">
    <div class="container home-hero-copy">
      <p class="kicker">Official archive / 음악 기록 보관소</p>
      <h1 class="display-xl home-title">Project UNAC</h1>
      <p class="lead home-lead">Austere records for a fictional world: serialized prose, sound, and image held on a black editorial surface. 세계관과 음악이 하나의 공식 기록으로 정리되는 밤의 아카이브.</p>
      <div class="hero-index" aria-label="Archive identity">
        <p><span>Discipline</span>World / Story / Sound</p>
        <p><span>Direction</span>Black canvas, sparse image, exact text</p>
      </div>
      <div class="button-row home-actions">
        <a class="button-primary" href="/world/">Enter the world</a>
        <a class="button-primary" href="/music/">Music by SHINHWI</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section home-archive-section">
    <div class="container editorial-grid home-archive-grid">
      <div class="section-head home-section-head">
        <p class="kicker">Second fold / 기록의 표면</p>
        <h2 class="display-lg">Archive surface</h2>
        <p class="body-copy">The homepage remains quiet by design. It introduces the work as an official threshold first, then lets each section open with measured hierarchy and documentary restraint.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="archive-lines" aria-label="Archive sections">
        <a class="archive-line" href="/world/">
          <span class="archive-label">World</span>
          <span>세계의 규칙, 인물, 연대기를 위한 공식 색인.</span>
        </a>
        <a class="archive-line" href="/story/">
          <span class="archive-label">Story</span>
          <span>문장으로 남겨진 장면과 연재 기록.</span>
        </a>
        <a class="archive-line" href="/music/">
          <span class="archive-label">Music</span>
          <span>SHINHWI의 사운드트랙과 원곡 아카이브.</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
